creator: Frank Peregrine
descriptionHtml: Experience a super realistic physics simulation made with stylish graphics and fun objects. You can build towers with different shaped blocks. Pick up and throw objects. Juggle objects with other objects, and even flip bottles. And there's a rag doll horse of coarse.
descriptionShort: Have fun with this realistic physics playground.
title: Physics Yeet Ragdoll Meme

descriptionHtml: Experience a fun, realistic physics simulation made with stylish graphics and fun objects. You can build towers with different shaped blocks. Pick up and throw objects.
